      <title>新西兰将废除世界首个烟草禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/new-zealand-set-scrap-world-first-tobacco-ban-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府表示，新西兰将于周二废除世界上第一部禁止向子孙后代销售烟草的法律，尽管研究人员和活动人士警告人们可能因此而死亡的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/new-zealand-set-scrap-world-first-tobacco-ban-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南计划进行工会改革以避免贸易困境，但冒着外国公司不安的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国官员和外交官表示，共产党统治下的越南预计将在今年批准联合国自由建立工会公约，此举旨在降低贸易争端风险，但可能会让一些外国公司感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国商飞将在东南亚5国展示C919、ARJ21飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-showcase-c919-arj21-jets-5-southeast-asian-countries-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司周二表示，将在五个东南亚国家进行C919和ARJ21喷气式飞机的飞行展示​​，为未来的国际销售奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-showcase-c919-arj21-jets-5-southeast-asian-countries-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:52:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚承诺在太平洋外交中为橄榄球提供更多资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/australia-pledges-more-funds-rugby-pacific-diplomacy-push-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚表示，将额外投入 1,420 万美元来促进太平洋岛屿参与橄榄球联盟，这是该地区外交努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sports/australia-pledges-more-funds-rugby-pacific-diplomacy-push-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰因毛利人抗议而关闭土著卫生当局</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-shut-indigenous-health-authority-amid-maori-protests-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰卫生部长周二表示，随着中右翼政府收回前几届政府的土著政策，新西兰毛利卫生局将于 6 月 20 日关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-shut-indigenous-health-authority-amid-maori-protests-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据富士电视台报道，日本首相岸田将于周二与 Meta 的扎克伯格讨论人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/japan-pm-kishida-discuss-ai-with-metas-zuckerberg-tuesday-fuji-tv-reports-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据富士电视台报道，日本首相岸田文雄将于周二会见 Meta Platforms 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格，就人工智能交换意见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/japan-pm-kishida-discuss-ai-with-metas-zuckerberg-tuesday-fuji-tv-reports-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：渣打银行暂停中国客户新的离岸渠道投资</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行表示，由于当地市场和货币疲软，海外投资需求激增，该行已暂停中国客户通过配额渠道对离岸产品进行新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-suspends-new-investments-clients-via-chinas-outbound-channel-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于医生罢工，韩国护士将承担更多医疗工作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-nurses-take-more-medical-work-due-doctor-walkout-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国卫生部长周二表示，韩国护士已获得法律保护，可以执行一些通常由医生进行的医疗程序，当局试图减轻实习医生罢工给医院工作人员造成的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-nurses-take-more-medical-work-due-doctor-walkout-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 02:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本通胀高于预期，亚洲股市动荡，交易员保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周二艰难上涨，日本通胀略高于预期，令投资者在本周欧洲和美国公布价格数据之前保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:59:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称5艘中国海警船进入前线岛屿附近海域</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾一位部长周二表示，在与北京的紧张关系持续升级之际，五艘中国海警船周一进入台湾前线金门岛周围的禁区或限制水域，但在被警告离开后不久就离开了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-5-china-coast-guard-ships-entered-waters-around-kinmen-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 01:23:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
